title: Jay Z attends start of trial over 1999 hit "Big Pimpin' "
text: > Entertainment Jay Z attends start of trial over 1999 hit "Big Pimpin'" FILE - In this Feb. 23, 2015 file photo, Jay Z arrives at the 2015 Vanity Fair Oscar Party in Beverly Hills, Calif. The rapper appeared in a Los Angeles federal court on Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015, for the start of a copyright infringement trial in which he and music producer Timbaland are accused of violating the rights of famed Egyptian composer Baligh Hamdi to create their 1999 hit "Big Pimpin'." (Photo by Evan Agostini/Invision/AP, File)
